<link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/product.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/custome.css">
<main class="product-page">
    <div class="product-images">
        <h3 class="title">Customize Your Own Jewelry</h3>
        <img src="/public/images/jewelryRing.jpg" alt="Custom Jewelry">
        
        <div style="margin: 20px;">
            <button class="add-item2" style="margin: 10px;">Save</button>
            <button class="add-item2" style="margin: 10px;">Share</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="product-details">
        <h3>Create Your Unique Style</h3>
        <h4>Discover the thrill of personalizing your own piece of jewelry with our
             'Customize Your Own Jewelry' option. Start your unique creation journey 
             by selecting your preferred precious metal - choose from either 
             high-quality gold or sterling silver. Add a touch of sparkle with your 
             choice of gemstone, from dazzling diamonds to vibrant rubies or serene 
             sapphires. Ensure the perfect fit with our customization sizing options, 
             and add a truly personal touch with our engraving service, allowing you 
             to inscribe a name, date, or special message. Your bespoke piece will be 
             carefully packaged in our custom boxes, perfect for gifting or safekeeping. 
             Our 'Customize Your Own Jewelry' is more than just a purchase; it's an 
             interactive experience that results in a one-of-a-kind piece, mirroring 
             your taste and encapsulating your story.
</h4>
        <p>Design:</p>
        <div class="customization-option">
            <input type="radio" name="style" value="Ring" id="ring"><label for="ring">Ring</label>
            <input type="radio" name="style" value="Necklace" id="necklace"><label for="necklace">Necklace</label>
            <input type="radio" name="style" value="Bracelet" id="bracelet"><label for="bracelet">Bracelet</label>
            <input type="radio" name="style" value="Earrings" id="earrings"><label for="earrings">Earrings</label>
        </div>

        <p>Gemstone:</p>
        <div class="customization-option">
            <input type="radio" name="jewel" value="Diamond" id="diamond"><label for="diamond">Diamond</label>
            <input type="radio" name="jewel" value="Ruby" id="ruby"><label for="ruby">Ruby</label>
            <input type="radio" name="jewel" value="Sapphire" id="sapphire"><label for="sapphire">Sapphire</label>
        </div>

        <label for="metal">Material:</label>
        <select name="metal" id="metal">
            <option value="Gold">Gold</option>
            <option value="Silver">Silver</option>
        </select>

        <label for="size">Size:</label>
        <select name="size" id="size">
            <option value="Small">Small</option>
            <option value="Medium">Medium</option>
            <option value="Large">Large</option>
        </select>

        <label for="engraving">Engraving:</label>
        <input type="text" name="engraving" id="engraving" maxlength="10" placeholder="Enter your text">

        <label for="packaging">Packaging:</label>
        <select name="packaging" id="packaging">
            <option value="Purple">Purple</option>
            <option value="Blue">Blue</option>
            <option value="Black">Black</option>
        </select>

        <div class="quantity-dropdown">
            <label for="quantity">Quantity:</label>
            <select name="quantity" id="quantity">
                <option value="1">1</option>
                <option value="2">2</option>
                <option value="3">3</option>
            </select>
        </div>

        <form action="/product/add-custom-item" method="POST" enctype="application/x-www-form-urlencoded">
            <button class="add-item">Add to cart </button>
        </form>
    </div>
</main>